{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And but-- but with my father, my father having lost all his savings at the very beginning of the war, all he could offer Schindler was his skills.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Schindler accepted that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think that somehow he respected this-- this relationship so that each time my father asked him for something, he would do it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He wasn't doing it because he-- my father had something else to offer him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So when he asked for my mother and me to be taken on, he only listened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had a terrific memory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He just remembered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we know that it was his doing that put my mother and me on the list.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then eventually, my sister, Aviva, who was returned from her company at about same time to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she would have been just in the general population and would have had about a 100 to one chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were five family members, five Leysons who survived the war in Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the end of the war, there were five of us there, my parents, my sister, my brother, and I.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "David.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who actually typed it, you mean?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, those people who did the-- the accounting for him and the-- there was some Jewish accountants that did some business work for him, bookkeepers and so on, those were the people who did the list.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There weren't many children in Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- for-- at one time, there was a person younger than I in-- in Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I was the youngest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was taken away, and I was the youngest in the company.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was the youngest one working in the factory along with the adults.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
